914
00:15:18,390 --> 00:15:19,379
There are all sorts of people
who manage that much.

915
00:15:20,192 --> 00:15:21,523
But still, that's a major

916
00:15:22,027 --> 00:15:23,051
deal for a high schooler.

917
00:15:23,429 --> 00:15:25,124
Yeah!  Aya, you have a gift for it!

918
00:15:25,564 --> 00:15:26,588
I'm sure you'll succeed!

919
00:15:26,999 --> 00:15:28,364
You're my pride and joy!

920
00:15:28,767 --> 00:15:30,530
I told you to stop encouraging
me from your heart like that !

921
00:15:31,170 --> 00:15:33,161
You're going to write a lot
now that it's summer, right?

922
00:15:33,639 --> 00:15:35,266
Yeah. I'm going to try writing something long.

923
00:15:36,642 --> 00:15:39,270
Besides, it's not like I'm the
only one doing something special.

924
00:15:39,879 --> 00:15:43,007
Tsubaki's a star volleyball player
who got to be a starter upon joining the team...

926
00:15:43,382 --> 00:15:44,940
...and Rika's always been good at Home Ec....

927
00:15:45,317 --> 00:15:47,251
...and makes these unbelievably
small, pretty things.

928
00:15:48,087 --> 00:15:49,076
Who knows in five or ten years.

929
00:15:50,055 --> 00:15:51,784
Everyone has something she's good at.

930
00:15:54,894 --> 00:15:56,691
That sounds so nice.

931
00:15:56,691 --> 00:15:58,155
You all have things you want to do.

932
00:15:58,697 --> 00:16:00,722
I've never even thought about it at all.

933
00:16:01,533 --> 00:16:02,557
That's so awesome.

934
00:16:03,002 --> 00:16:04,731
I can't do anything besides get good grades.

935
00:16:05,271 --> 00:16:08,104
What's wrong with getting
nothing but good grades?

936
00:16:12,511 --> 00:16:14,035
Well, shall we split up here?

937
00:16:16,382 --> 00:16:18,777
Oh, what is it, Tsubasa?
Don't want to go home yet?

939
00:16:19,184 --> 00:16:20,481
What is it? You want to play a bit more?

940
00:16:21,854 --> 00:16:24,220
You're too easy on her, Yukino!

942
00:16:24,590 --> 00:16:26,852
Tsubasa's really taken a liking to you.

943
00:16:27,259 --> 00:16:30,729
But when she latches onto you like that,
she won't let go until the bitter end.

945
00:16:30,729 --> 00:16:33,323
I'll tell you now that
you're really in for it.

947
00:16:33,799 --> 00:16:36,928
We don't want to go along with her whims,
so we're outta here.

949
00:16:36,928 --> 00:16:39,033
Anyways, don't get carried away!

951
00:16:39,471 --> 00:16:40,335
We'll call later. See ya!

952
00:16:42,341 --> 00:16:44,172
I know. I have to go with you, right?

953
00:16:46,378 --> 00:16:48,676
Tsubasa's really gotten
attached to Yukino, hasn't she?

954
00:16:49,081 --> 00:16:51,611
