to someone like that.

956
00:16:52,151 --> 00:16:54,176
Well, she's having a pretty
hard time these days.

957
00:16:54,653 --> 00:16:55,813
I hope being friends with Yukino

958
00:16:56,221 --> 00:16:57,313
helps her get over things...

959
00:16:58,023 --> 00:17:00,184
I heard her father might get remarried?

960
00:17:00,626 --> 00:17:02,594
Yeah. She has a father complex going,

961
