of those faith healers or something.

968
00:17:14,907 --> 00:17:16,875
Hey, I wonder why Tsubasa 

969
00:17:17,343 --> 00:17:18,867
wanted to stay with Yukino so badly just now.

971
00:17:19,445 --> 00:17:22,345
Who knows? Probably because
she doesn't want to be home much.

972
00:17:22,815 --> 00:17:23,747
I bet it feels really awkward there.

973
00:17:24,883 --> 00:17:26,942
But she WILL go home later, won't she?

974
00:17:27,686 --> 00:17:30,215
She wouldn't be thinking of
anything weird, would she?

976
00:17:33,792 --> 00:17:34,656
Yukinon!

977
00:17:40,966 --> 00:17:42,627
Grades aren't everything.

978
00:17:43,202 --> 00:17:45,834
They all have so much individuality.

980
00:17:46,338 --> 00:17:48,898
This is no good. I'm totally clueless.

981
00:17:49,575 --> 00:17:52,066
While I was out being a nerd
without any second thoughts...

982
00:17:52,511 --> 00:17:54,411
...everyone else was finding
out about so much more.

983
00:17:54,913 --> 00:17:57,006
I never even noticed it until now.

984
00:17:57,449 --> 00:17:59,280
I feel like I got left behind.

985
00:17:59,952 --> 00:18:02,582
Feeling insecure?
That's not like you.

987
00:18:03,022 --> 00:18:06,924
But I just realized how inadequate
I've been all this time.

989
00:18:07,993 --> 00:18:10,291
So you'll be finding out starting now.

990
00:18:10,662 --> 00:18:13,561
You realized that grades aren't
the only yardstick for people.

992
00:18:14,133 --> 00:18:15,657
