998
00:18:25,165 --> 00:18:29,278
Yeah, yeah, yeah!
Friendship!

999
00:18:29,815 --> 00:18:31,481
I have friends. The loneliness
fades away just because of that.

1000
00:18:31,481 --> 00:18:34,981
I'm not alone anymore.

1001
00:18:35,554 --> 00:18:36,680
I have friends.

1002
00:18:40,793 --> 00:18:41,817
Wow, what a huge bag.

1003
00:18:42,327 --> 00:18:43,760
What are you going to do with that, Tsubasa?

1004
00:18:44,830 --> 00:18:45,626
