1012
00:18:58,444 --> 00:19:01,211
He never even said a word about
getting remarried to me before.

1014
00:19:01,747 --> 00:19:02,873
It looks like he's serious.

1015
00:19:03,782 --> 00:19:04,771
This got heavy all of a sudden.

1016
00:19:05,250 --> 00:19:06,478
I've never seen her talk this much before.

1017
00:19:06,952 --> 00:19:10,812
He was taken in by her because
he's so absent minded and naive!

1019
00:19:11,890 --> 00:19:13,448
It's so disgusting!

1020
00:19:13,792 --> 00:19:14,781
I won't have it!

1021
00:19:15,227 --> 00:19:18,120
