do that kind of thing?!

1025
00:19:22,501 --> 00:19:23,832
That's why I'm running away.

1026
00:19:24,269 --> 00:19:27,231
I'm sure Daddy will open
his eyes when I'm gone.

1028
00:19:27,739 --> 00:19:31,573
This is a battle to take
Daddy back from that woman.

1030
00:19:32,611 --> 00:19:34,306
But if you run away, where will you go?

1031
00:19:35,347 --> 00:19:36,245
With you.

1032
00:19:38,217 --> 00:19:41,050
I can't go along with you
that far! No, I'm going home!

1033
00:19:42,754 --> 00:19:44,915
Friendship!  Friendship!

1034
00:19:46,291 --> 00:19:49,385
Arima, friendship is a wonderful thing.

1035
00:19:49,928 --> 00:19:52,226
But every so often, it's rough.

1036
00:20:53,315 --> 00:20:54,213
What'll happen next!

1037
00:20:54,783 --> 00:20:57,410
Sis got caught up in some
other family's personal problems.

1039
00:20:57,852 --> 00:20:59,342
And our guests keep bringing

1040
00:20:59,721 --> 00:21:00,585
up crisis after crisis!

1041
00:21:00,956 --> 00:21:03,049
What happened to the
heart-warming comedy?!

1042
00:21:03,458 --> 00:21:05,016
Next time on KareKano:

1043
00:21:05,360 --> 00:21:06,418
"Where Happiness is."

1044
